	Shipper and Transporter have agreed to a rate other than the maximum rate, rates shall be Transporter's maximum rates and charges plus all applicable surcharges in effect from time to time
	under the applicable Rate Schedule (as&nbsp;stated above) on file with the Commission unless otherwise agreed to by the parties in writing. Provisions governing a Rate other than the maximum shall
	be set forth in this Paragraph&nbsp;9 and/or on Appendix&nbsp;B&nbsp;hereto.

	This
	Agreement shall incorporate and in all respects be subject to the "General Terms and Conditions" and the applicable Rate Schedule (as&nbsp;stated above) set forth in Transporter's FERC Gas
	Tariff, Third Revised Volume No.&nbsp;1, as may be revised from time to time. Transporter may file and seek Commission approval under Section&nbsp;4 of the Natural Gas Act (NGA) at any time and
	from time to time to change any rates, charges or provisions set forth in the applicable Rate Schedule (as&nbsp;stated above) and the "General Terms and Conditions" in Transporter's FERC Gas Tariff,
	Third Revised Volume No.&nbsp;1, and Transporter shall have the right to place such changes in effect in accordance with the NGA, and this Agreement shall be deemed to include such changes and any
	such changes

<FONT COLOR="#0C2E82" SIZE=2>
<B>
	TRANSPORTATION SERVICE AGREEMENT
<BR>
	Contract Identification FT18147
</B>
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	This
	Transportation Service Agreement (Agreement) is entered into by Great Lakes Gas Transmission Limited Partnership (Transporter) and ANR PIPELINE COMPANY (Shipper).
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	WHEREAS,
	Shipper has requested Transporter to transport Gas on its behalf and Transporter represents that it is willing to transport Gas under the terms and conditions of
	this&nbsp;Agreement.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	NOW,
	THEREFORE, Transporter and Shipper agree that the terms below constitute the transportation service to be provided and the rights and obligations of Shipper and
	Transporter.
</FONT>
</P>
<DL COMPACT>
<DT STYLE='FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;MARGIN-BOTTOM:-11PT;'>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	1.
</FONT>
</DT>
<DD STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">

	EFFECTIVE DATE:
</B>
</FONT>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;November 01, 2016
<BR>
<BR>
</FONT>
</DD>
<DT STYLE='FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;MARGIN-BOTTOM:-11PT;'>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	2.
</FONT>
</DT>
<DD STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">

<FONT SIZE=2>

</B>
</FONT>
<FONT SIZE=2>

</DD>
</DL>

	Unless
	Shipper and Transporter have agreed to a rate other than the maximum rate, rates shall be Transporter's maximum rates and charges plus all applicable surcharges in effect from time to time
	under the applicable Rate Schedule (as&nbsp;stated above) on file with the Commission unless otherwise agreed to by the parties in writing. Provisions governing a Rate other than the maximum shall
	be set forth in this Paragraph&nbsp;9 and/or on Appendix&nbsp;B&nbsp;hereto.
</FONT>
</P>
</UL>

</FONT>

<FONT SIZE=2>
	12.
</FONT>
</DT>
<DD STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
<B>
	INCORPORATION OF TARIFF INTO AGREEMENT:
</B>
</FONT>
</DD>
</DL>
<UL>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	This
	Agreement shall incorporate and in all respects be subject to the "General Terms and Conditions" and the applicable Rate Schedule (as&nbsp;stated above) set forth in Transporter's FERC Gas
	Tariff, Third Revised Volume No.&nbsp;1, as may be revised from time to time. Transporter may file and seek Commission approval under Section&nbsp;4 of the Natural Gas Act (NGA) at any time and
	from time to time to change any rates, charges or provisions set forth in the applicable Rate Schedule (as&nbsp;stated above) and the "General Terms and Conditions" in Transporter's FERC Gas Tariff,
	Third Revised Volume No.&nbsp;1, and Transporter shall have the right to place such changes in effect in accordance with the NGA, and this Agreement shall be deemed to include such changes and any
	such changes
</FONT>
</P>
</UL>

<UL>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	which
	become effective by operation of law and Commission Order, without prejudice to Shipper's right to protest the&nbsp;same.
</FONT>
</P>
</UL>
<DL COMPACT>
<DT STYLE='FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;MARGIN-BOTTOM:-11PT;'>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	13.
</FONT>
</DT>
<DD STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
<B>
	MISCELLANEOUS:
</B>
</FONT>
</DD>
</DL>
<UL>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	No
	waiver by either party to this Agreement of any one or more defaults by the other in the performance of this Agreement shall operate or be construed as a waiver of any continuing or future
	default(s), whether of a like or a different character.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	Any
	controversy between the parties arising under this Agreement and not resolved by the parties shall be determined in accordance with the laws of the State of&nbsp;Michigan.
</FONT>
</P>
</UL>
<DL COMPACT>
<DT STYLE='FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;MARGIN-BOTTOM:-11PT;'>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	14.
</FONT>
</DT>
<DD STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
<B>
	OTHER PROVISIONS:
</B>
</FONT>
</DD>
</DL>
<UL>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	It
	is agreed that no personal liability whatsoever shall attach to, be imposed on or otherwise be incurred by any Partner, agent, management official or employee of the Transporter or any director,
	officer or employee of any of the foregoing, for any obligation of the Transporter arising under this Agreement or for any claim based on such obligation and that the sole recourse of Shipper under
	this Agreement is limited to assets of the Transporter.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	Upon
	termination of this Agreement, Shipper's and Transporter's obligations to each other arising under this Agreement, prior to the date of termination, remain in effect and are not being terminated
	by any provision of this&nbsp;Agreement.
</FONT>
</P>
</UL>

<P ALIGN="CENTER" STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">

<FONT SIZE=2>
<B>
<!-- COMMAND=ADD_TXTHEX,"PMS287" -->
</B>
</FONT>
<FONT COLOR="#0C2E82" SIZE=2>
<B>
	TRANSPORTATION SERVICE AGREEMENT
<BR>
	Contract Identification FT18150
</B>
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	This
	Transportation Service Agreement (Agreement) is entered into by Great Lakes Gas Transmission Limited Partnership (Transporter) and ANR PIPELINE COMPANY (Shipper).
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	WHEREAS,
	Shipper has requested Transporter to transport Gas on its behalf and Transporter represents that it is willing to transport Gas under the terms and conditions of
	this&nbsp;Agreement.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	NOW,
	THEREFORE, Transporter and Shipper agree that the terms below constitute the transportation service to be provided and the rights and obligations of Shipper and
	Transporter.
</FONT>
</P>
<DL COMPACT>
<DT STYLE='FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;MARGIN-BOTTOM:-11PT;'>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	1.
</FONT>
</DT>
<DD STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
<B>
	EFFECTIVE DATE:
</B>
</FONT>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;November 01, 2016
<BR>
<BR>
</FONT>
</DD>
<DT STYLE='FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;MARGIN-BOTTOM:-11PT;'>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	2.
</FONT>
</DT>
<DD STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
<B>
	CONTRACT IDENTIFICATION:
</B>
</FONT>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;FT18150
<BR>
<BR>
</FONT>
</DD>
<DT STYLE='FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;MARGIN-BOTTOM:-11PT;'>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	3.
</FONT>
</DT>
<DD STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
<B>
	RATE SCHEDULE:
</B>
</FONT>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;FT
<BR>
<BR>
</FONT>
</DD>
<DT STYLE='FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;MARGIN-BOTTOM:-11PT;'>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	4.
</FONT>
</DT>
<DD STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
<B>
	SHIPPER TYPE:
</B>
</FONT>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Interstate Pl
<BR>
<BR>
</FONT>
</DD>
<DT STYLE='FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;MARGIN-BOTTOM:-11PT;'>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	5.
</FONT>
</DT>
<DD STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
<B>
	STATE/PROVINCE OF INCORPORATION:
</B>
</FONT>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Delaware
<BR>
<BR>
</FONT>
</DD>
<DT STYLE='FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;MARGIN-BOTTOM:-11PT;'>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	6.
</FONT>
</DT>
<DD STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
<B>
	TERM:
</B>
</FONT>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;November 01, 2014 to October&nbsp;31, 2017
<BR>
<BR>
</FONT>
</DD>
<DT STYLE='FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;MARGIN-BOTTOM:-11PT;'>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	7.
</FONT>
</DT>
<DD STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
<B>
	EFFECT ON PREVIOUS CONTRACTS:
</B>
</FONT>
</DD>
</DL>
<UL>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	This
	Agreement supersedes, cancels and terminates, as of the effective date stated above, the following contract(s): Service Agreement dated November 01, 2015 with Contract Identification FT18150.
</FONT>
</P>
</UL>
<DL COMPACT>
<DT STYLE='FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;MARGIN-BOTTOM:-11PT;'>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	8.
</FONT>
</DT>
<DD STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
<B>
	MAXIMUM DAILY QUANTITY (Dth/Day):
</B>
</FONT>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;101,300
</FONT>
</DD>
</DL>
<UL>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	Please
	see Appendix&nbsp;A for further detail.
</FONT>
</P>
</UL>
<DL COMPACT>
<DT STYLE='FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;MARGIN-BOTTOM:-11PT;'>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	9.
</FONT>
</DT>
<DD STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
<B>
	RATES:
</B>
</FONT>
</DD>
</DL>
<UL>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	Unless
	Shipper and Transporter have agreed to a rate other than the maximum rate, rates shall be Transporter's maximum rates and charges plus all applicable surcharges in effect from time to time
	under the applicable Rate Schedule (as&nbsp;stated above) on file with the Commission unless otherwise agreed to by the parties in writing. Provisions governing a Rate other than the maximum shall
	be set forth in this Paragraph&nbsp;9 and/or on Appendix&nbsp;B&nbsp;hereto.
</FONT>
</P>
</UL>
<DL COMPACT>
<DT STYLE='FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;MARGIN-BOTTOM:-11PT;'>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	10.
</FONT>
</DT>
<DD STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
<B>
	POINTS OF RECEIPT AND DELIVERY:
</B>
</FONT>
</DD>
</DL>
<UL>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	The
	primary receipt and delivery points are set forth on Appendix&nbsp;A.
</FONT>
</P>
</UL>
<DL COMPACT>
<DT STYLE='FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;MARGIN-BOTTOM:-11PT;'>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	11.
</FONT>
</DT>
<DD STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
<B>
	RELEASED CAPACITY:
</B>
</FONT>
</DD>
</DL>
<UL>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	N/A
</FONT>
</P>
</UL>
<DL COMPACT>
<DT STYLE='FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;MARGIN-BOTTOM:-11PT;'>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	12.
</FONT>
</DT>
<DD STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
<B>
	INCORPORATION OF TARIFF INTO AGREEMENT:
</B>
</FONT>
</DD>
</DL>
<UL>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	This
	Agreement shall incorporate and in all respects be subject to the "General Terms and Conditions" and the applicable Rate Schedule (as&nbsp;stated above) set forth in Transporter's FERC Gas
	Tariff, Third Revised Volume No.&nbsp;1, as may be revised from time to time. Transporter may file and seek Commission approval under Section&nbsp;4 of the Natural Gas Act (NGA) at any time and
	from time to time to change any rates, charges or provisions set forth in the applicable Rate Schedule (as&nbsp;stated above) and the "General Terms and Conditions" in Transporter's FERC Gas Tariff,
	Third Revised Volume No.&nbsp;1, and Transporter shall have the right to place such changes in effect in accordance with the NGA, and this Agreement shall be deemed to include such changes and any
	such changes
</FONT>
</P>
</UL>

<P STYLE='FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;PAGE-BREAK-BEFORE:ALWAYS'>
</P>

<UL>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	which
	become effective by operation of law and Commission Order, without prejudice to Shipper's right to protest the&nbsp;same.
</FONT>
</P>
</UL>
<DL COMPACT>
<DT STYLE='FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;MARGIN-BOTTOM:-11PT;'>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	13.
</FONT>
</DT>
<DD STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
<B>
	MISCELLANEOUS:
</B>
</FONT>
</DD>
</DL>
<UL>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	No
	waiver by either party to this Agreement of any one or more defaults by the other in the performance of this Agreement shall operate or be construed as a waiver of any continuing or future
	default(s), whether of a like or a different character.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	Any
	controversy between the parties arising under this Agreement and not resolved by the parties shall be determined in accordance with the laws of the State of&nbsp;Michigan.
</FONT>
</P>
</UL>
<DL COMPACT>
<DT STYLE='FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;MARGIN-BOTTOM:-11PT;'>
<FONT SIZE=2>
	14.
</FONT>
</DT>
<DD STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
<B>
	OTHER PROVISIONS:
</B>
</FONT>
</DD>
</DL>
<UL>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	It
	is agreed that no personal liability whatsoever shall attach to, be imposed on or otherwise be incurred by any Partner, agent, management official or employee of the Transporter or any director,
	officer or employee of any of the foregoing, for any obligation of the Transporter arising under this Agreement or for any claim based on such obligation and that the sole recourse of Shipper under
	this Agreement is limited to assets of the Transporter.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;">
<FONT SIZE=2>
	Upon
	termination of this Agreement, Shipper's and Transporter's obligations to each other arising under this Agreement, prior to the date of termination, remain in effect and are not being terminated
	by any provision of this&nbsp;Agreement.
</FONT>
</P>
</UL>
<DL COMPACT>
<DT STYLE='FONT-FAMILY:ARIAL;MARGIN-BOTTOM:-11PT;'>

	15.
</FONT>
</DT>

</B>

	notices and communications with respect to this Agreement shall be in writing by mail, e-mail, or fax, or other means as agreed to by the parties, and sent to the addresses stated below or to any
	other such address(es) as may be designated in writing by mail, e-mail, or fax, or other means similarly agreed&nbsp;to:
</FONT>
</P>
</UL>
